# Metallic Shimmers Textile Paper Metallics (TPM) Sheet

## A full sheet of dazzling metallic color for Fashion, Home + Interiors

Sku#: SWTPM

$ 17.50

Color Number

Select Color Number

![Pantone Color Viewer](https://www.pantone.com/media/color-finder/img/chips/pantone-color-chip-blank.webp)

Add To Cart

Use these large-format sheets to wrap your products in 200 new metallic finishes, for realistic color representation and verification. Ideal for product designers and brand owners, Pantone’s Metallic Shimmers Sheets offer versatile visualization of luxurious, trend-driven metallics and can also be chipped for communication and specification.

- View metallic finishes on product in three dimensions and at large scale
- Can be cut to create large-scale palettes for viewing at a distance
- One Metallic Shimmers Color per 21.6 x 28 cm sheet
- Printed gridlines on the back for creating up to 80 2.54 x 2.54 cm chips

All Swatch Cards are non-returnable/non-refundable.

